verbose_text: They identified haptoglobin related protein (HPR) from serum samples of patients with mycoplasma pneumonia by a SNA-I pull-down assay and further confirmed elevated SNA-I expression in the mycoplasma pneumonia and viral pneumonia groups versus the bacterial pneumonia group.131 The serum levels of Mac-2 binding protein (M2BP) and M2BPGi, a specific glycoform recognized by WFA, are positively correlated with liver fibrosis progression.
